<head><title>
</title>Making mf run on fc5</head>
</body>
<ul>
<li> this assumes that you have /usr/share/texmf/metafont/config/mf.ini
hanging around somewhere..
<li>mf -ini /usr/share/texmf/metafont/config/mf.ini (as root)
<li>this means you can use \mode:=mf
</ul>
